title: Real photo postcard with Ten Million
author: seattlerainiers

posts.post_title: Real photo postcard with Ten Million
posts.post_content:
Very rare 1910 RPPC of University of Washington baseball team, including Ten Million of 1911 Obak fame. Squad includes other Northwest athletic notables, including Wee Coyle. Ten is bottom row, far right.

Look here for more information on Ten and his mates:

[url]http://sportspressnw.com/2122105/2011/wayback-machine-seattles-first-athletic-ambassadors[/url]

Pinholes in top corners.

Would prefer to trade this card for something NW or West Coast related, but am open to other ideas.
